name: mocado
description:
feeling of being underrated, being hidden from somewhere...
-
This piece is from the collection "descartável", which is a audiovisual project that I discarded bad feelings and turned it into something that could heal me. The project addresses mental health issues, self knowledge and it was a opportunity to me to study animation. This is the 20th piece of the collection.
